From 2bc66a0180ca39ae05c922c1698cba54ea5a48ff Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vasu Bhatia <git@vbh.ai>
Date: Mon, 27 Apr 2026 13:34:52 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] eink: add E-Ink display settings and button config

EinkSettingsFragment provides refresh mode, cold/warm frontlight,
keyboard backlight, and a force-refresh action, all applied live via
EinkManagerService. EinkButtonConfigFragment lets the user assign one
of thirteen actions to each of the three button gestures and tune the
double-press and long-press timing. Wired into Display settings as a
new E-Ink category.

Change-Id: I6debd4f068645334137517ea081d50e970a0626d
